      • setNamespaces

        public FandomSearchOptions setNamespaces(java.lang.String namespaces)
        Sets the namespaces the search algorithm is supposed to be looking for.

        Example:
        0|1|2
        (for namespace 0, 1 and 2)

        Use "*" for all namespaces.

        Parameters:
